      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GEMMA KEEPING (2) is yet to miss the placings in an excellent record this trip which boasts four wins and four placings. Placed last time (30.07) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 5.5 lengths. Looks a leading chance on best. FROM THE DISCO (1) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (30.09) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including 10 wins. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. GREENER PASTURES (5) boasts a strong record this course with four wins and four minors from 12 tries. Placed last time (29.99) at this track in a Grade 4/5, finishing third and beaten 5 lengths. With even luck and a clean start should be thereabouts. ZIPPER IN (8) should be thereabouts despite an unplaced run here most recently.",
